@startuml
title Viaverse Conversation / Message State — State Diagram

[*] --> CONVERSATION_OPEN
CONVERSATION_OPEN --> ACTIVE : participants valid
ACTIVE --> LOCKED : job closed/dispute
LOCKED --> ACTIVE : reopened
LOCKED --> ARCHIVED : retention/archive

[*] --> MESSAGE_DRAFT
MESSAGE_DRAFT --> SCANNING : send
SCANNING --> SENT : safe
SCANNING --> HELD_FOR_REVIEW : needs review
HELD_FOR_REVIEW --> SENT : approved
HELD_FOR_REVIEW --> BLOCKED : rejected
SENT --> DELIVERED : recipient reached
DELIVERED --> READ : opened

ARCHIVED --> [*]
READ --> [*]
BLOCKED --> [*]

note bottom
Conversation state and message state are separate.
A locked conversation may remain readable but not writable;
dispute/support export can still be policy-controlled.
end note
@enduml
